title: 01 OSHO HINDI AUDIOS A-D amr files
description:
Osho Hindi audio files,in Alphabetic sequence from A_D 3,75 GB

Series of Adhyatma Upanishad, spoken on Mt. Abu 1971-72,
have Hindi and English talks.(Don't be surprised if it switch suddenly to English.. all is OK.
 
Osho spoke Hindi in the morning and English in the afternoon.

File format = AMR.

The Adaptive Multi-Rate audio codec is an audio compression format optimized for speech ..Many modern mobile telephone handsets can store short audio recordings It can be played on pc with VLC and MPC player without converting.

search corresponding books in Hindi and some are translated to English. See on oshoworld(dot)com and download free
